Matthew,

	If you use the Naming Time Negation Keyword, the experimenter
can decide whether the response was correct, and enters this information
on the keyboard.  You could then use Branch If Wrong to go back.  I
haven't tried this, but it seems that it should work.

	--k.i.f.


